### 2ï¸âƒ£ Basic protocol sequencing (6â€“8)

Examples:

* IDLE â†’ SETUP
* SETUP â†’ ACCESS (next cycle mandatory)
* ACCESS â†’ IDLE or SETUP
* PENABLE only high when PSEL is high
* No skipping SETUP phase

ğŸ‘‰ **~7 assertions**

